flowchart TB
    subgraph Authentication
      Login[User Login] --> Validate{Valid?}
      Validate -->|Yes| Token[Generate Token]
      Validate -->|No| Error[Show Error]
    end
    
    subgraph Authorization
      Token --> CheckRole{Check Role}
      CheckRole -->|Admin| AdminDash[Admin Dashboard]
      CheckRole -->|User| UserDash[User Dashboard]
      CheckRole -->|Guest| GuestView[Guest View]
    end
    
    subgraph DataAccess
      AdminDash --> DB[(Database)]
      UserDash --> DB
      GuestView --> Cache[(Cache)]
      Cache --> DB
    end
    
    Error --> Login
    DB --> Response[Send Response]
    Response --> End((End))